---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    
    <title>GK360 | Pakistan's Premium CSS, PMS & General Knowledge Academy</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Master PPSC, FPSC, and NTS exams with GK360. Access solved past papers with logical explanations, topic-wise MCQs, and premium video lectures." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="PPSC past papers, FPSC preparation, CSS MCQs, PMS notes, NTS past papers, Pakistan government jobs" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://gk360.pk" />

    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://gk360.pk" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="GK360 | Master Your PPSC & FPSC Exams" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Stop memorizing blindly. Get solved past papers with detailed logical explanations and secure your government job." />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://gk360.pk/social-preview.jpg" />

    <meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta property="twitter:title" content="GK360 | Master Your PPSC & FPSC Exams" />
    <meta property="twitter:description" content="Stop memorizing blindly. Get solved past papers with detailed logical explanations." />

    <script type="application/ld+json">
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "EducationalOrganization",
        "name": "GK360",
        "url": "https://gk360.pk",
        "logo": "https://gk360.pk/logo.png",
        "description": "Pakistan's premium online academy for PPSC, FPSC, and CSS preparation featuring solved past papers and conceptual MCQs.",
        "sameAs": [
          "https://facebook.com/gk360",
          "https://youtube.com/gk360"
        ]
      }
    </script>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  
  <body class="bg-dots text-ink min-h-screen flex flex-col" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;">
    
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-20">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center cursor-pointer">
            <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">GK360<span class="text-accent">.pk</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 items-center font-bold text-slate-600">
            <a href="/papers" class="hover:text-accent transition">Past Papers</a>
            <a href="/notes" class="hover:text-accent transition">Study Notes</a>
            <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-accent transition">Blog</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-4">
            <a href="#" class="font-bold text-slate-600 hover:text-ink transition">Sign In</a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-ink text-paper px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition duration-200">Join Free</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="flex-grow">
      <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs md:text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-600 mb-8 shadow-sm">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></span> Complete 2026 Syllabus Setup
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-900">
          Crack Any Govt Exam. <br class="hidden md:block"/> 
          Study <span class="highlight-text text-slate-900">Smarter</span>, Not Harder.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium px-4">
          The ultimate productivity-focused preparation hub for <strong class="text-slate-900">FPSC, PPSC, SPSC, KPPSC, BPSC,</strong> and <strong class="text-slate-900">NTS</strong>. Stop blindly memorizing. Master concepts with logical explanations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 px-4">
          <a href="#papers" class="bg-accent text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-teal-800 transition shadow-lg shadow-teal-900/20 text-lg sm:w-auto w-full text-center hover:-translate-y-1">Start Practicing Free</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="papers" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-10">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">Latest Past Papers</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">Fully solved with detailed logical breakdowns.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/papers" class="hidden sm:inline-block font-bold text-accent hover:text-teal-800 transition">View All Papers &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
          <a href="#" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-100 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(226,232,240,1)] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(226,232,240,1)] transition-all">
            <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-md uppercase tracking-wide">PPSC</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-4 mb-2 text-slate-900">Tehsildar (BS-16) - 2023</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">100 MCQs • English & General Knowledge</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-100 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(226,232,240,1)] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(226,232,240,1)] transition-all">
            <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-md uppercase tracking-wide">FPSC</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-4 mb-2 text-slate-900">Inspector Customs (BS-16) - 2024</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">100 MCQs • Everyday Science & Math</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-100 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(226,232,240,1)] hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_rgba(226,232,240,1)] transition-all">
            <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-md uppercase tracking-wide">PPSC</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mt-4 mb-2 text-slate-900">Lecturer Education (BS-17) - 2022</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">100 MCQs • Subject Specialist</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <a href="/papers" class="sm:hidden block text-center bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl">View All Papers</a>
      </section>

      <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="relative z-10 md:w-2/3">
            <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-yellow-900 text-xs font-extrabold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 inline-block">Free Resources</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Download High-Yield Cheat Sheets</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 font-medium mb-8 text-lg">We condensed massive textbooks into 2-page PDF summaries. Download our most popular timeline maps and vocabulary lists for rapid revision.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
              <a href="#" class="bg-white text-slate-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
                📄 Pak Affairs Timeline (1857-1947)
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="bg-white/10 text-white border border-slate-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-white/20 transition">
                📄 Everyday Science Formulas
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 text-[15rem] leading-none opacity-5 transform translate-x-1/4 translate-y-1/4 select-none pointer-events-none">📘</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 mb-12">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-10">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">Study Strategy & Updates</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">Science-backed techniques to clear competitive exams.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/blog" class="hidden sm:inline-block font-bold text-accent hover:text-teal-800 transition">Read All Articles &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
          <a href="#" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
            <div class="h-48 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl mb-4 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-4xl group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">⏰</div>
            <p class="text-accent font-bold text-sm mb-2">Productivity</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 leading-tight">How to Study for PPSC with a Full-Time Government Job</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium line-clamp-2">Learn the time-blocking methods used by active officers to prepare for their next promotion exams without burning out.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
            <div class="h-48 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl mb-4 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-4xl group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">🗺️</div>
            <p class="text-accent font-bold text-sm mb-2">Syllabus Guide</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 leading-tight">The 80/20 Rule for Pakistan Studies: What to Actually Read</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium line-clamp-2">Stop reading entire history books. Here are the exact eras and events that make up 80% of all commission questions.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="block bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
            <div class="h-48 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl mb-4 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-4xl group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-300">🧠</div>
            <p class="text-accent font-bold text-sm mb-2">Memory Science</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 leading-tight">Using Spaced Repetition for Everyday Science MCQs</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium line-clamp-2">How to use the forgetting curve to your advantage and permanently memorize vitamins, planets, and chemical formulas.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
        <a href="/blog" class="sm:hidden block text-center bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl">Read All Articles</a>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-white border-t border-slate-200 mt-auto">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
          <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">GK360<span class="text-accent">.pk</span></span>
            <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm mt-2">Pakistan's Premium Preparation Platform.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex space-x-6 text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-ink transition">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-ink transition">Terms of Service</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-ink transition">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 mt-8 pt-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-slate-400 font-medium text-sm">
            &copy; 2026 GK360.pk. All rights reserved. <br class="sm:hidden"/>
            <span class="inline-block mt-2 sm:mt-0 sm:ml-2 text-slate-500 font-bold hover:text-accent transition duration-200 cursor-pointer">
              Crafted with ❤️ by Abraaj Growth Labs
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>